						<p><div class="item">
<h2><a class="listing" style="link" href="/en/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Developments/East-African-cassava-research-gets-major-funding-boost" title="East African cassava research gets major funding boost " alt="link">East African cassava research gets major funding boost </a></h2>

	
					<p>Three projects targeting the deadly viral cassava diseases, cassava brown streak disease (CBSD) and cassava mosaic disease (CMD), have received a financial boost for research and development focused on developing resistant varieties in Eastern Africa. The multimillion dollar funding for cassava research aims to boost sharing of disease-resistant seed. The advanced technologies to be developed will help accelerate and increase the accuracy of breeding programmes.&nbsp;Read SciDevNet’s report:<a href="http://www.scidev.net/en/sub-suharan-africa/news/east-african-cassava-research-gets-major-funding-boost-1.html" target="_self">http://www.scidev.net/en/sub-suharan-africa/news/east-african-cassava-research-gets-major-funding-boost-1.html</a>(SciDev, 18/12/2012)See also: <b><a href="http://liferay.iita.org/web/iita/2012-press-releases/-/asset_publisher/CxA7/content/cassava-varieties-developed-by-iita-show-promise-of-tackling-famine-in-the-horn-of-africa;jsessionid=D1135CB66FCFB1D0074005137A58C733?redirect=%2Fweb%2Fiita%2F2012-press-releases" target="_blank">Cassava varieties developed by IITA show promise of tackling famine in the Horn of Africa&nbsp;</a></b></p>
							<p><span class="date">22/05/2013</span></p>
	<div class="cnt">
	<a class="link" href="/en/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Developments/East-African-cassava-research-gets-major-funding-boost">Read more...</a>
</div>
<br class="cl">
</div>
